{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And by doing so, he even made it worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The-- the fracture became a break, and I was in terrible pain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The reason I'm telling this story is because my arm went on until the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It went on for quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It went on for-- it seemed like forever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because in Warsaw, they set my arm straight, which was already starting to heal wrongly because time has elapsed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So my arm never got a chance to be set.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they put me in a cast, which they told me to keep on X amount of time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I remember coming home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was very uncomfortable, because it started itching, and it seemed like there were worms under the-- under the plaster.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I developed a very good weapon against the children, [LAUGHS] all the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because if they would come close to me, I would threaten them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I'm going to hit them with my-- with my cast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Well, it seemed that when they took off the plaster, my arm was not healed properly, and they had to go back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And that's when the war was already on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I remember my father taking me to Warsaw when the war was on, and how the Germans didn't let us get into the-- into the-- it's either was a train or a bus or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they-- they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they made us sit somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember, but I remember they were very stern.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And this was just in the beginning, very beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was still-- I'm pretty sure it was still 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And Ostrowiec was-- Poland was just invaded on-- on September 1.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
